---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Cris - UX Designer with AI training background based in Z√ºrich. Creating intuitive digital experiences through user research and modern development tools."
>
  <!-- Hero Section with Photo -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Photo -->
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="relative max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0">
            <!-- Colorful shape behind -->
            <div class="absolute -inset-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/20 via-purple-200 to-pink-200 rounded-[3rem] rotate-3"></div>
            <img
              src="/images/Cris.jpg"
              alt="Cris - UX Designer"
              class="relative z-10 w-full rounded-2xl shadow-large"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Intro -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-accent/10 rounded-full mb-6">
            <span class="text-body-sm font-medium text-accent">About Me</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="text-h1-mobile md:text-h1 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-6 leading-tight">
            Bridging design and development with AI
          </h1>

          <p class="text-body-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            I'm Cris, a UX designer based in Z√ºrich who does Vibe Coding - combining user-centered design with AI-powered development to create intuitive digital experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience Section - With Background -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32 bg-secondary/30">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h3 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-12">Experience</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-h4 font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">UX Design</h3>
              <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                Worked in design agencies on projects for companies like <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Atupri</span>, focusing on complex UX challenges like simplifying insurance comparisons and creating intuitive product selection flows.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-h4 font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">AI Training & Evaluation</h3>
              <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                Specialized in training and evaluating generative AI models, particularly large language models (LLMs). As a native Italian linguist with professional English skills, I ensure AI outputs are accurate, safe, well-structured, and culturally appropriate.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-purple-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-accent/20">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-h4 font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Vibe Coding</h3>
              <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                Today, I combine user-centered design principles with AI-powered development to build products from concept to launch.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beyond Work -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h3 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-12">Beyond Work</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 bg-secondary/50 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-body font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">üê± Misu the Cat</h3>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            My fluffy companion and unofficial design critic who judges all my work from the desk corner.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-secondary/50 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-body font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">üì∫ Seinfeld Enthusiast</h3>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Currently on rewatch #100+. Still finding new jokes I missed.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-secondary/50 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-body font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">üç´ Chocolate Explorer</h3>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Systematically working through Z√ºrich's chocolate shops, one praline at a time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-secondary/50 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-body font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">üáÆüáπ Language Teacher</h3>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Certified teacher of Italian as a foreign language. Parliamo italiano!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Currently - CTA Section -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-purple-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h3 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Currently</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <p>
          I specialize in training and evaluating generative AI models, combining language expertise with AI alignment. In Italian, I handle the full evaluation process - prompt creation, output assessment, response rewriting, and RLHF contributions. In English, I focus on evaluating outputs and delivering actionable insights.
        </p>
        <p>
          My UX design background brings a user-centered perspective to AI evaluation, considering usefulness, user intent, and overall communication quality.
        </p>
        <p class="text-h4 font-semibold text-text-primary !mt-12">
          Open to opportunities in generative AI model evaluation, responsible AI development, and UX design roles in Z√ºrich.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="mailto:effe.christina@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-accent text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-dark transition-colors duration-300 text-body font-medium">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          effe.christina@gmail.com
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
